---
title: Pulled Chicken Sliders Tangy Cabbage Slaw
description: Southern barbecue is famous for its tangy, vinegar-based sauce. Balanced by a touch of brown sugar and tossed with juicy pulled chicken, this barbecue sauce will have you ditching the bottled kind. A little bit of slaw on the sliders is an essential addition.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5979fc4c51d3f1760d69e3e2-adf35ca6.jpg
